Package edu.first.identifiers

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Input
    The general contract for classes which give back an input.
    Output
    The general contract for classes that output to something.
    Position
    A position that has two possible states: on and off.
    PositionalActuator
    The general contract for classes that actuate to a position.
    PositionalSensor
    The general contract for classes that can access the position of something.
    RateActuator
    The general contract for classes that actuate to a rate.
    RateSensor
    The general contract for classes that can access the rate of something.
    Switch
    A switch is a manipulatable state with 2 possible values: on and off.
